---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import ContactSection from "../components/ContactSection.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="About | Roman & Co">
    <Header />

    <main class="bg-[#efefef] pt-10 md:pt-14">
        <section class="mx-auto max-w-[1880px] px-4 md:px-6">
            <div class="pt-10 md:pt-14">
                <div class="border-y border-dotted border-black/35">
                    <div class="grid gap-0 xl:grid-cols-[1.15fr_0.85fr]">
                        <div class="px-0 py-8 md:py-10 xl:pr-10">
                            <p
                                class="text-[18px] font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.01em] text-[#7b7b7b]"
                            >
                                About
                            </p>

                            <h1
                                class="mt-6 max-w-[900px] text-[52px] font-medium uppercase leading-[0.92] tracking-[-0.05em] text-[#2f2f37] md:text-[92px]"
                            >
                                The strategists behind the conversation
                            </h1>
                        </div>

                        <div
                            class="border-l border-dotted border-black/35 px-6 py-8 md:px-8 md:py-10"
                        >
                            <p
                                class="text-[18px] font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.01em] text-[#7b7b7b]"
                            >
                                Our Mission
                            </p>

                            <div
                                class="font-mono-custom mt-6 max-w-[760px] text-[20px] leading-[1.35] text-[#3a3a44] md:text-[23px]"
                            >
                                <p>
                                    Roman & Co was built on a simple belief:
                                    marketing should create clarity, not noise.
                                </p>

                                <p class="mt-5">
                                    We help brands position themselves
                                    strategically, communicate with precision,
                                    and grow through a deep understanding of
                                    consumer behavior, not trends or short-term
                                    tactics.
                                </p>

                                <p class="mt-5">
                                    Our mission is to build brands that are
                                    trusted, memorable, and structurally strong
                                    across industries, stages, and markets.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div
                    class="mt-14 grid gap-10 xl:grid-cols-[0.95fr_1.05fr] xl:gap-14"
                >
                    <div>
                        <p
                            class="text-[18px] font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.01em] text-[#7b7b7b]"
                        >
                            Our Story
                        </p>

                        <div
                            class="font-mono-custom mt-6 max-w-[780px] text-[20px] leading-[1.35] text-[#3a3a44] md:text-[23px]"
                        >
                            <p>
                                Roman & Co was created by two brothers with a
                                shared passion for business, marketing, and
                                startups.
                            </p>

                            <p class="mt-5">
                                After years of working across tech, eCommerce,
                                healthcare, and retail, from early-stage
                                startups to global companies, we saw the same
                                pattern: most brands struggle not because of
                                execution, but because of positioning and
                                strategic clarity.
                            </p>

                            <p class="mt-5">
                                We founded Roman & Co to bridge that gap.
                            </p>

                            <p class="mt-5">
                                By combining behavioral psychology, market
                                intelligence, and hands-on growth experience, we
                                work with brands that value long-term strength
                                over short-term spikes.
                            </p>

                            <p class="mt-8">
                                We don’t chase trends.
                                <br />
                                We build foundations.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-[24px] bg-[#d8e5ef]">
                        <img
                            src="/caresyntax-small-1.jpg"
                            alt="Roman & Co team visual"
                            class="block h-[360px] w-full object-cover md:h-[560px] xl:h-[760px]"
                        />
                    </div>
                </div>

                <section class="mt-20">
                    <div class="grid gap-10 xl:grid-cols-[260px_1fr] xl:gap-10">
                        <div class="pl-6 md:pl-10 xl:pl-14">
                            <h2
                                class="max-w-[210px] text-[52px] font-medium uppercase leading-[0.9] tracking-[-0.05em] text-[#2f2f37] md:text-[64px]"
                            >
                                Meet the Team
                            </h2>
                        </div>

                        <div class="max-w-[920px]">
                            <div class="grid gap-6 xl:grid-cols-2">
                                <article
                                    class="flex min-h-[760px] flex-col justify-between rounded-[24px] border border-black/5 bg-[#ece8e8] px-7 pb-8 pt-7 md:px-8 md:pb-9 md:pt-8"
                                >
                                    <div>
                                        <div
                                            class="flex items-start justify-between gap-4"
                                        >
                                            <div>
                                                <h3
                                                    class="font-mono-custom text-[28px] leading-[1.1] text-[#3a3a44] md:text-[31px]"
                                                >
                                                    Călin Roman
                                                </h3>

                                                <p
                                                    class="mt-3 text-[18px] font-medium text-[#2f2f37] md:text-[19px]"
                                                >
                                                    Head of Strategy
                                                </p>
                                            </div>

                                            <div class="text-[#f0b2f5]">
                                                <svg
                                                    viewBox="0 0 64 64"
                                                    class="h-11 w-11"
                                                    fill="none"
                                                    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                                                >
                                                    <path
                                                        d="M22 50H42M32 14C26.4772 14 22 18.4772 22 24C22 28.4183 24.8657 32.1672 28.8333 33.4896V38H25C23.3431 38 22 39.3431 22 41V50H42V41C42 39.3431 40.6569 38 39 38H35.1667V33.4896C39.1343 32.1672 42 28.4183 42 24C42 18.4772 37.5228 14 32 14Z"
                                                        stroke="currentColor"
                                                        stroke-width="2.5"
                                                        stroke-linecap="round"
                                                        stroke-linejoin="round"
                                                    ></path>
                                                    <path
                                                        d="M27 24H37M27 28H35"
                                                        stroke="currentColor"
                                                        stroke-width="2.5"
                                                        stroke-linecap="round"
                                                    ></path>
                                                </svg>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>

                                        <div
                                            class="mt-8 border-t border-dashed border-black/35 pt-8"
                                        >
                                            <div
                                                class="font-mono-custom max-w-[355px] text-[18px] leading-[1.42] text-[#3a3a44] md:text-[20px]"
                                            >
                                                <p>
                                                    Călin leads strategy with a
                                                    strong focus on positioning,
                                                    consumer psychology, and
                                                    performance.
                                                </p>

                                                <p class="mt-6">
                                                    With experience across tech
                                                    startups, healthcare,
                                                    eCommerce, and retail, he
                                                    combines market intelligence
                                                    with hands-on execution to
                                                    design growth systems that
                                                    are both creative and
                                                    measurable.
                                                </p>

                                                <p class="mt-6">
                                                    He works at the intersection
                                                    of narrative, data, and
                                                    behavior.
                                                </p>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>

                                    <a
                                        href="#"
                                        class="mt-10 inline-flex h-[48px] w-fit items-center rounded-full bg-[#e7a6ee] px-6 text-[17px] font-medium uppercase tracking-[-0.01em] text-[#2d2431] transition hover:opacity-90"
                                    >
                                        Linkedin
                                        <span
                                            class="ml-2 text-[22px] leading-none"
                                            >×</span
                                        >
                                    </a>
                                </article>

                                <article
                                    class="flex min-h-[760px] flex-col justify-between rounded-[24px] border border-black/5 bg-[#ece8e8] px-7 pb-8 pt-7 md:px-8 md:pb-9 md:pt-8"
                                >
                                    <div>
                                        <div
                                            class="flex items-start justify-between gap-4"
                                        >
                                            <div>
                                                <h3
                                                    class="font-mono-custom text-[28px] leading-[1.1] text-[#3a3a44] md:text-[31px]"
                                                >
                                                    Alex Roman
                                                </h3>

                                                <p
                                                    class="mt-3 text-[18px] font-medium text-[#2f2f37] md:text-[19px]"
                                                >
                                                    Head of Performance
                                                </p>
                                            </div>

                                            <div class="text-[#f0b2f5]">
                                                <svg
                                                    viewBox="0 0 64 64"
                                                    class="h-11 w-11"
                                                    fill="none"
                                                    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                                                >
                                                    <path
                                                        d="M22 46L42 18M42 18H30M42 18V30M22 18L42 46M22 46H34M22 46V34"
                                                        stroke="currentColor"
                                                        stroke-width="2.5"
                                                        stroke-linecap="round"
                                                        stroke-linejoin="round"
                                                    ></path>
                                                </svg>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>

                                        <div
                                            class="mt-8 border-t border-dashed border-black/35 pt-8"
                                        >
                                            <div
                                                class="font-mono-custom max-w-[355px] text-[18px] leading-[1.42] text-[#3a3a44] md:text-[20px]"
                                            >
                                                <p>
                                                    Alex oversees performance
                                                    strategy and growth systems.
                                                </p>

                                                <p class="mt-6">
                                                    He builds and optimizes
                                                    acquisition funnels, paid
                                                    campaigns, and tracking
                                                    infrastructures that drive
                                                    scalable results. Focused on
                                                    metrics, experimentation,
                                                    and efficiency, he ensures
                                                    every marketing decision is
                                                    backed by data.
                                                </p>

                                                <p class="mt-6">
                                                    Performance is not
                                                    guesswork. It’s engineering.
                                                </p>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>

                                    <a
                                        href="#"
                                        class="mt-10 inline-flex h-[48px] w-fit items-center rounded-full bg-[#e7a6ee] px-6 text-[17px] font-medium uppercase tracking-[-0.01em] text-[#2d2431] transition hover:opacity-90"
                                    >
                                        Linkedin
                                        <span
                                            class="ml-2 text-[22px] leading-none"
                                            >×</span
                                        >
                                    </a>
                                </article>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </section>
            </div>
        </section>

        <div class="mt-16 md:mt-20">
            <ContactSection />
        </div>

        <Footer />
    </main>
</BaseLayout>
